<item>
            <title>[LU-10007] Update health resource agents</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10007</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;healthLUSTRE&lt;/tt&gt; uses &lt;tt&gt;/proc/fs/lustre/health_check&lt;/tt&gt; directly instead of using &lt;tt&gt;lctl&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Both &lt;tt&gt;healthLUSTRE&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;healthLNET&lt;/tt&gt; should load &lt;tt&gt;lustre&lt;/tt&gt; module otherwise they return failures if they start before other lustre services.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
